    <item>
      <title>新加坡房屋销售飙升至十年新高，引发遏制担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/singapore-home-sales-surge-to-decade-high-stoking-curb-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡房屋销售量跃升至十多年来的最高水平，证实了房地产市场的复苏，并引发了人们对政府将进一步出台调控措施的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/singapore-home-sales-surge-to-decade-high-stoking-curb-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 04:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vortexa 称美国制裁中断了伊朗原油对中国的出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/us-sanctions-disrupt-iranian-crude-flows-to-china-vortexa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Vortexa Ltd. 称，由于美国对油轮实施更大范围的制裁，伊朗对中国的原油出口受到干扰，导致流向这个 OPEC 产油国最重要客户的石油供应减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/us-sanctions-disrupt-iranian-crude-flows-to-china-vortexa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 04:27:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰计划改革，让地方议会发挥核心作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/new-zealand-plans-reforms-to-focus-local-councils-on-core-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰政府敦促地方议会专注于核心任务，不要将稀缺的资金用于会议中心或中央政府负责的项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/new-zealand-plans-reforms-to-focus-local-councils-on-core-role</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 04:20:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国领导人称明年年底可能举行选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/bangladesh-interim-leader-says-election-possible-by-late-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国临时领导人表示，该国计划在 2025 年底至 2026 年上半年举行全国大选，这是该国在今年早些时候陷入政治动荡后，其政府首次提供选举路线图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/bangladesh-interim-leader-says-election-possible-by-late-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 04:19:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
