      <title>泰国将于本周就缅甸问题举行非正式会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/thailand-to-host-informal-talks-on-strife-torn-myanmar-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，泰国将主办东南亚国家联盟非正式会议，讨论缅甸战乱的最新局势及未来发展方向。]]></description>
