      <title>数据令人失望，中国主要债券收益率创下历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/china-s-key-bond-yield-hits-fresh-record-low-as-data-disappoints</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一系列疲软的经济数据提振了对避险资产的需求，中国 10 年期主权债券收益率周一跌至历史新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/china-s-key-bond-yield-hits-fresh-record-low-as-data-disappoints</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 03:31:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港市区重建局将签署 17 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/hong-kong-s-urban-renewal-authority-to-sign-hk-13-billion-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，香港市区重建局将与一组银行获得一笔 130 亿港元（17 亿美元）的五年期贷款，这是该局十多年来首次获得银团贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/hong-kong-s-urban-renewal-authority-to-sign-hk-13-billion-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 03:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
